info.name: 10FastFingers Dark Mode - 10FF (Bruhdooh) v1.4
info.description:
Some other person made a joke of a Dark Mode for 10FastFingers so I took the time to completely recolor the entire website. Hopefully this will suffice but I will continue to edit this in the future and also make more themes.

If you have any issues or you see that anything is wrong, please message me on Discord: @Bruhdooh#2984
info.additionalInfo:
Version 1.0: Released Dark Mode 9/19/2018.
Version 1.1: Changed the font of the typing area.
Version 1.2: Removed the "top x%" on the WPM box. Changed the color of wrong words on the WPM box. Removed the "can you type faster" badge in the Share Your Result box.
Version 1.3: Fixed the Competition Box results, it now matches with the theme. Thanks to Bailey for finding this one.
Version 1.4: Updated the Profile page colors. Now things are a lot more readable.
